174
00:06:56,340 --> 00:06:57,100
Let's call it jerk,

175
00:06:57,100 --> 00:06:57,400
j.

176
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:01,980
Which is derivative of acceleration with respect to time.

177
00:07:02,360 --> 00:07:02,880
Alright,

178
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:05,000
now we have to differentiate the right-hand side.

179
00:07:05,180 --> 00:07:06,700
The right-hand side is a product.

180
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,780
To differentiate a product,

181
00:07:08,780 --> 00:07:10,640
