00:20:11,080 --> 00:20:11,960
I did it right,

531
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,340
but I didn't say it right.

532
00:20:13,760 --> 00:20:16,360
The derivative of the square is twice

533
00:20:16,360 --> 00:20:18,960
the something times the derivative of the something.

534
00:20:19,760 --> 00:20:20,540
All right?

535
00:20:20,840 --> 00:20:22,160
That gets rid of the factor of two.

536
00:20:23,000 --> 00:20:26,080
So the time derivative of the kinetic energy

