00:20:42,500 --> 00:20:44,160
So we might as well call it the acceleration.

544
00:20:47,040 --> 00:20:48,420
a sub i.

545
00:20:48,780 --> 00:20:50,220
Ith component of acceleration.

546
00:20:51,340 --> 00:20:53,890
Let's calculate the time derivative

547
00:20:53,890 --> 00:20:56,440
now of the potential energy.

548
00:20:56,720 --> 00:20:58,660
And the potential energy is also...

