00:21:22,099 --> 00:21:23,560
you move in the x direction.

562
00:21:23,800 --> 00:21:24,910
It varies a little bit if

563
00:21:24,910 --> 00:21:26,020
you move in the y direction.

564
00:21:26,340 --> 00:21:27,540
It varies a little bit if

565
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,740
you move in the z direction.

566
00:21:30,040 --> 00:21:30,980
And so in fact,

567
00:21:30,980 --> 00:21:33,220
the derivative of u with respect

568
00:21:33,220 --> 00:21:35,460
to t is the sum of terms,

569
00:21:37,879 --> 00:21:41,659
each term being the derivative of u with

570
00:21:41,659 --> 00:21:45,440
respect to x times the time derivative of x,

