01:05:12,240 --> 01:05:14,020
We could express this as a differential equation.

1684
01:05:14,220 --> 01:05:14,520
We will.

1685
01:05:14,660 --> 01:05:16,080
As a differential equation,

1686
01:05:16,680 --> 01:05:20,780
which basically says that the difference in the slope

