1688
01:05:23,360 --> 01:05:25,420
But it's quite obvious that what it says

1689
01:05:25,420 --> 01:05:27,340
within this little red region here

1690
01:05:27,340 --> 01:05:29,220
is just go straight ahead.

1691
01:05:30,020 --> 01:05:32,740
If you generalize that all along the curve,

1692
01:05:32,900 --> 01:05:34,320
it will tell you at every point,

